      *****************************************************************         
      **                                                                        
      **   MQSERIES COMPLETION & REASON CODE ROUTINES FOR BATCH.                
      **   USE IN CONJUCTION WITH ISWS002.                                      
      **   CICS VERSION OF THIS IS ISPD005.                                     
      **                                                                        
      *****************************************************************         
       9001-MQSERIES-ERROR.                                                     
                                                                                
           PERFORM  VARYING IS-COMPLETION FROM 1 BY 1                           
                      UNTIL PV-COMPLETION-CODE                                  
                          = IS-COMPLETION-CODE (IS-COMPLETION)                  
                         OR IS-COMPLETION >= IS-COMPLETION-MAX                  
               CONTINUE                                                         
           END-PERFORM.                                                         
           IF IS-COMPLETION >= IS-COMPLETION-MAX                                
               MOVE IS-COMPLETION-MAX TO IS-COMPLETION.                         
                                                                                
           CALL IS-MQCHECK USING PV-REASON                                      
                                 IS-REASON-TEXT.                                
                                                                                
           DISPLAY '*** MQSERIES ERROR: '   PV-ACTION.                          
           DISPLAY '    COMPLETION CODE = ' PV-COMPLETION-CODE                  
                   ' - ' IS-COMPLETION-CODE-DESC (IS-COMPLETION).               
           DISPLAY '             REASON = ' PV-REASON                           
                   ' - ' IS-REASON-TEXT.                                        
           MOVE PV-REASON TO PV-ABEND-CODE.                                     
           CALL 'ILBOABN0' USING PV-ABEND-CODE.                                 
